{"tid":59938,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"亞博館對日歌手YOSHIKI今晚活動極大保留：未收到法例文件","createTime":"2016-12-30T05:20:25.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-30T05:44:29.000Z","uid":48093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d12f8f29f48c3c3a82ac1b9503dcec80646f2e9c","tid":59938,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:20:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161230/large/1483074283_ec56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161230%2Flarge%2F1483074283_ec56.jpg&h=c9e30ffc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本樂隊X JAPAN靈魂人物YOSHIKI原定昨晚(29/12)於亞洲博覽館舉行世界巡迴音樂會《YOSHIKI Classical Special with Orchestra &ndash; HONG KONG》，但由於主辦單位未能就活動取得相關牌照，亞博館指經與主辦單位磋商後，決定取消昨晚活動。<br />\n<br />\n亞博館今日(30/12)早上發出鄭重聲明，指至今仍然未收到主辦單位擬於今晚舉辦的音樂活動所需要的相關法例文件，「因此亞博館對於有關活動能否如期舉行存有極大保留」。亞博館指，為免計劃參與活動的人士失望，已要求主辦單位盡快交代有關活動能否如期舉行。<br />\n<br />\n亞博館強調所有活動必須符合相關法例規定，以確保公眾安全及活動順利舉行。"},{"pid":"837ca60c792e73594009ea799af6f2f414736b0e","tid":59938,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:43:34.000Z","msg":"X from Hong Kong<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63f4e1e5c76fa226460648edf66d4b617110fee5","tid":59938,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:44:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>X from Hong Kong<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n利伸，唔識欣賞X Japan d 歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}